    <item>
      <title>法官质疑美国为何阻止为马杜罗律师提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/nyregion/maduro-venezuela-court-manhattan.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府阻止委内瑞拉支付尼古拉斯·马杜罗的辩护律师费用。在一次听证会上，一名法官反复表示，前总统为自己辩护的权利“至关重要”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/nyregion/maduro-venezuela-court-manhattan.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 21:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股市创伊朗战争爆发以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/business/oil-stock-gas-prices-iran.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心战争何时结束，标准普尔 500 指数周四下跌 1.7%，油价继续上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/business/oil-stock-gas-prices-iran.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 21:04:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在通过协议拉拢特朗普后，巴基斯坦在谈判桌上获得一席之地</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/us/politics/trump-pakistan-iran.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交特使史蒂夫·威特科夫（Steve Witkoff）利用和平委员会宣布了一项协议，该协议可能会夷平巴基斯坦拥有的曼哈顿酒店。目前该国正参与与伊朗的和平谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/us/politics/trump-pakistan-iran.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 20:48:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
