      <title>南达科他州州长签署法案，要求提供公民身份证明才能投票</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/us/south-dakota-voting-proof-of-citizenship.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该法律反映了共和党的全国优先事项，要求新登记的选民证明他们是美国公民，以便在州或地方竞选中投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/26/us/south-dakota-voting-proof-of-citizenship.html</guid>
